      <title>法国主要政党在电视辩论中就经济、移民问题发生冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/france-s-main-parties-clash-on-economy-immigration-in-tv-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国三大政治党派的领导人首次电视辩论中就退休、税收和移民等各个问题发生冲突，他们试图让选民相信他们值得信任，可以管理欧洲第二大经济体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/france-s-main-parties-clash-on-economy-immigration-in-tv-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 21:44:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Einhorn 的 Greenlight 在新诉讼中抨击“宏观主管”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/einhorn-s-greenlight-slams-head-of-macro-in-fresh-lawsuit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大卫·艾因霍恩 (David Einhorn) 旗下的 Greenlight Capital Inc. 与一名前雇员展开了法律纠纷，该前雇员自称是该公司的宏观交易主管，指控詹姆斯·菲什巴克 (James Fishback) 实际上是一个表现不佳的人员，并在被解雇前辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/einhorn-s-greenlight-slams-head-of-macro-in-fresh-lawsuit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 21:30:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
